oai_dc:dc.dc:title: SHORE PROTECTION ON THE COAST OP "YAIZU"
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Seo, Goichi
Fukuchi, Tatsuma
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: shore protection
Yaizu
beach erosion
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This report describes the history of beach erosion and the countermeasures against it extending over the last few centuries on the coast of "YAIZU" Pishing Port. It also includes a study on the causes of erosion by analysing geographical, topographical and oceanogrphical conditions of the coastal area.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 10 (1966): Proceedings of 10th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Tokyo, Japan, 1966.; 66
